  "title": "Trying to toggleRefinement() multiple facets",
  "body": "I'm trying to toggleRefinement multiple values while creating a custom widget:\r\n```\r\n...\r\ninit: function init(options) {\r\n   var helper = options.helper;\r\n   helper.toggleRefinement(attributeName, ['facet1,facet2']);\r\n}\r\n...\r\n```\r\nBut they are returning no results, can you not use conjunctive faceting of the same category with multiple values?",
